originalText: The sound system we've set up ::Laughs.:: It's really good.
The pay is pretty good here. Considering everything and all, you know?
The new screens we've got. ::Smiles.:: You can't miss the scoreboard now.
The last race was absolutely insane. Can't wait for some more.
We've had some... incidents in the past.
I've heard that there are some sick bets going on for this race. ::Nods.::
Core City would wish to have something like this, ha!
We put a lot of effort into this one. ::Points to the racing track.::
The fences had to go up. People were going insane about the hoppers. ::Laughs.::
Good thing there are so many hoppers out there.
Hop over to the Betmaker. Take your chances and then... ::Smiles and nods.::
Pirates are all over the place. They freak me out, you know. ::Grips the weapon.::
The Rig is in shambles, who would've guessed. Hpmh, if we were there, it would've been intact.
You wanna hear a joke? What do hoppers do with a piece of paper? Rip it, rip it. ::Grunts.::
A snake of sorts is wriggling and churning up the waters. Can you believe that?
I can't wait for the race to start.
Come on, come on, start the damned thing already.
Why is it taking them so long to get the show going?
I dig this place quite a bit.
We need this over at the Core City.
::Swipes the air.:: Come on, come on!
I could watch this aaaall day... ::Smiles.::
Darn it, I wanted to see more.
That was a hell of a race!
Back to home now I guess... ::Shrugs.::
I'll be back here for sure.
I kinda sensed they'd call it off.
Gotta grease my vocal cords. ::Smiles and takes a sip.::
Don't you see I'm readying up?
Hopperdrome will witness a glorious race today. ::Nods.::
With me behind the mic, let me tell you, there's going to be some mad fire on the tracks. ::Laughs.::
::Turns off the mic.:: Do I need to call the guards on you?
::Covers the mic with his left hand.:: Just stop, okay?
::Turns around and makes a mean face.::
That was intense. ::Wipes sweat off of his forhead.::
Can't wait to commentate on next one. ::Smiles.::
We had to call it off. ::Shrugs.::
I was so ready to commentate the race... Oh well.
Something went down with the hoppers. It's all canceled now.
Guess we gotta go back to catching some hoppers. Wish we had a race before that.
Talk to the Betmaker, not me. ::Sighs.::
Stay in line. ::Points at the ground.::
Ugh... do I have to do this?
Only the personnel can step in here.
I hate this shift. ::Shakes her head.::
I'll need a new round of drinks soon. ::Nods.::
One day I'll get a hopper for myself.
I'd never imagine myself here a few years back. Oh well.
Locked up and good to go. Uhh, Poor things...
After what's happened over at The Rig, all guns here are justified.
::Glances at you and then faces away.::
That... son of a rat... owes me...
Who's the new... Invu- :: Hic:: -tus? ::Spits on the ground.::
I'm not going... back to that damned mine ag-again ::Burps.::
I'm *tryin'* to watch the damn race!
